# {{project}}

A TypeScript library generated with [`@osdk/create-app`](https://www.npmjs.com/package/@osdk/create-app).

## Local development

```sh
npm install
npm run build
```

Write your library code under `src/`. The `src/index.ts` file is the package entrypoint, and whatever it exports is the public API of the library. Tests live alongside the source in `src/**/__tests__`.

## Scripts

- `npm run build` — type-check and emit ESM + declaration files to `dist/` with `tsc`.
- `npm test` — run the test suite with [Vitest](https://vitest.dev).
- `npm run check` — check formatting and lint with [Ultracite](https://www.npmjs.com/package/ultracite) (oxlint + oxfmt).
- `npm run fix` — auto-fix formatting and lint issues.

Only the compiled output in `dist/` is included when the package is published.
